DESCRIPTION:What will YOU Discover? Join our 4 online events to hear from f
	aculty\, learn about programs\, and explore career pathways that interest 
	you.\n\nMonday\, March 9\, 4:00 p.m. to 5:15 p.m. Health and Medical Educa
