BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:8Sq-Jkd_zfKlFwxDzAZUW
SUMMARY:Baking Fundamentals: Cookies\, Cakes\, Custards and More
DTSTAMP:20260307T065923Z
DTSTART:20260318T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Would you like to be able to make a variety of beautiful and de
	licious baked treats with confidence? Gain fundamental skills and knowledg
	e for baking in this hands-on class.\n\nWe will learn about ingredients\, 
	interactions\, and techniques\, using a variety of mixing methods\, recipe
	s\, and best practices. And we will make a broad range of yummy foods\, su
	ch as muffins\, biscuits\, sponges\, chiffons\, angel food cakes\, quiche\
	, pâte à choux\, custards\, crèmes\, pastry doughs\, pies\, tarts\, layer 
	cakes\, frostings\, meringue\, buttercreams\, and specialty desserts.\n\nE
	njoy making delectable baked goods\, both sweet and savory. We will also d
	iscuss alternative ingredients for people with restrictive diets\, food se
	nsitivities\, and food allergies.\n\nTake advantage of the large\, well-eq
	uipped kitchen at Seattle Central's Culinary Academy. Learn some of the mo
	st useful tips from an experienced chef\, and develop practices for workin
	g in a clean\, safe\, and efficient way.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/e
	vents/#/details/baking-fundamentals-cookies-cakes-custards-and-more/177552
	04/2026-03-17T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/baking-fundamentals-cooki
	es-cakes-custards-and-more/17755204/2026-03-17T00
LOCATION:Seattle Central College Continuing Education\, 1701 Broadway\, Sea
	ttle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
